    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold as a project car or for parts. The engine runs roughly with a noticeable knock and several active fluid leaks, and the transmission is slipping significantly between gears. The exterior has substantial rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, while the interior upholstery is heavily worn and the air conditioning is non-functional. It is not currently reliable for daily use and will likely need to be towed.",
